tags.description: A small park in the middle of Oakmont hills. It has three ponds for fishing and the three ponds are connected via small waterfalls. It has a sidewalk around the outside to walk and view the ponds from.
A small park for people to let their dogs and kids play, currently has lighting in the trees for after dark safety.
